    <string name="mission_text">To empower farmers across Maharashtra and India with smart, accessible soil health estimation using just a smartphone photo. By combining image analysis, geolocation data, and machine learning, we aim to make soil testing affordable and instant for every farmer.</string>
    <string name="research_background">Research Background</string>
    <string name="research_text">This app is part of an ongoing PhD research project focused on digital soil analysis. Data has been collected from farms across Maharashtra, trained using MobileNetV2-based deep learning models, and validated against standard laboratory soil test results from ICAR.</string>
